398
00:32:46,233 --> 00:32:47,473
But in my world,

399
00:32:48,293 --> 00:32:49,513
Today

400
00:32:49,963 --> 00:32:50,833
is the 24th.

401
00:32:53,043 --> 00:32:53,883
